َ","meaning":"perhaps/maybe (with emphasis)","transliteration":"laʿalla","root":"","lemmaId":4735},{"id":"65:1:37","ayahNum":1,"wordNum":37,"word":"ٱللَّهَ","meaning":"Allah (as the object being feared in وَٱتَّقُوا۟)","transliteration":"l-laha","root":"أله","lemmaId":650},{"id":"65:1:38","ayahNum":1,"wordNum":38,"word":"يُحْدِثُ","meaning":"he causes (something) to happen","transliteration":"yuḥ'dithu","root":"حدث","lemmaId":null},{"id":"65:1:39","ayahNum":1,"wordNum":39,"word":"بَعْدَ","meaning":"after","transliteration":"baʿda","root":"بعد","lemmaId":null},{"id":"65:1:40","ayahNum":1,"wordNum":40,"word":"ذٰلِكَ","meaning":"that, that one (pointing to something far)","transliteration":"dhālika","root":"","lemmaId":1677},{"id":"65:1:41","ayahNum":1,"wordNum":41,"word":"أَمْرًا","meaning":"a command/matter (that Allah brings about)","transliteration":"amran","root":"أمر","lemmaId":null},{"id":"65:2:1","ayahNum":2,"wordNum":1,"word":"فَإِذَا","meaning":"And then when","transliteration":"fa-idhā","root":"","lemmaId":null},{"id":"65:2:2","ayahNum":2,"wordNum":2,"word":"بَلَغْنَ","meaning":"they (feminine) reached (referring to divorced women reaching the end of their waiting period)","transliteration":"balaghna","root":"بلغ","lemmaId":null},{"id":"65:2:3","ayahNum":2,"wordNum":3,"word":"أَجَلَهُنَّ","meaning":"their (f) appointed time/term (subject of بَلَغْنَ)","transliteration":"ajalahunna","root":"أجل","lemmaId":null},{"id":"65:2:4","ayahNum":2,"wordNum":4,"word":"فَأَمْسِكُوهُنَّ","meaning":"then hold/keep them (feminine)!","transliteration":"fa-amsikūhunna","root":"مسك","lemmaId":null},{"id":"65:2:5","ayahNum":2,"wordNum":5,"word":"بِمَعْرُوفٍ","meaning":"with kindness/properly (describing how to part ways in فَارِقُوهُنَّ)","transliteration":"bimaʿrūfin","root":"عرف","lemmaId":null},{"id":"65:2:6","ayahNum":2,"wordNum":6,"word":"أَوْ","meaning":"or (connecting فَأَمْسِكُوهُنَّ with فَارِقُوهُنَّ)","transliteration":"aw","root":"","lemmaId":4642},{"id":"65:2:7","a